The paper deals with formal verification of neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of several sub-fields of computer science. However, given that the paper proposes a novel framework for designing an effective branching strategy for Branch and Bound (BaB) formulation, which involves learning a graph neural network (GNN), it is most likely to be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, since the paper deals with convolutional neural networks, it could also be classified under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, since the paper deals with safety-critical areas, it could also be classified under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
